    nlinarith [abs_nonneg (nth_partial i f x)]
```

So we have shown that each term $|(y_i - x_i) \cdot (\partial_i f)(x)| \leq \varepsilon \cdot |(\partial_i f)(x)|$.

Now, we can sum over all $i$:

$\sum_i |(y_i - x_i) \cdot (\partial_i f)(x)| \leq \sum_i \varepsilon \cdot |(\partial_i f)(x)| = \varepsilon \cdot \sum_i |(\partial_i f)(x)|$.

Let's complete the formal proof:

```tactics
