```tactics

private noncomputable
def interpolated_deriv {n : ℕ} (x y : E n) (f : E n → ℝ) (t : ℝ) : ℝ :=
  ∑ i, (y i - x i) * nth_partial i f ((1 - t) • x + t • y)
```

